      "text": "I was in a-- I don't know if you know so much straw, a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was in the-- in the-- Then I-- I yield.",
