    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and I didn't-- I didn't have the children [INAUDIBLE] was alone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I came in the night, and I was waiting.",
