      "text": "So she came out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she thought [INAUDIBLE] she, when I got my children, I come to the town to my [NON-ENGLISH], to my mother over there in hospital.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So she brought me diapers for the children to the hospital then you see was the-- I-- anyway.",
